short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Chromium extension to see who has recently visited your Facebook profile

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
1 - Install the extension.
2 - Login to your facebook profile
3 - Refresh your browser to reload your profile page.
4 - Click on the extension icon and it will show you the users that have recently interacted with your profile or content.

Note: The application does not take any of your data, it only uses the same data that facebook sends when you request your profile information, the extension sorts this data and offers it to you in a nice and interactive way.
